headlines.shortLinkText: Terry Rozier shines as Hornets beat Thunder 134-116

headlines.shortLinkText: Antetokounmpo, Bucks rally past Jazz for 117-111 victory

events.name: Toronto Raptors at Los Angeles Lakers

headlines.description: — Scottie Barnes scored 15 of his 21 points in the first quarter and the Toronto Raptors held off a late rally by the Los Angeles Lakers for a 114-103 victory Monday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Barnes, Raptors all over Lakers early in 114-103 win
